    "deskripsi_bisnis": "PT Bhakti Multi Artha Tbk, through its subsidiaries, provides management consulting services in Indonesia. It provides advice and guidance for business operational, organization issues and other management matters; and various management functions, agronomist and agricultural economics management consulting in agriculture and similar sector, design of accounting methods, and procedures, as well as accounting program. The company offers group insurance products comprising of national credit life, national personal accident, national eka life, and national welfare fund protection products, as well as life insurance. In addition, the company provides group additional insurance, such as group critical illness, permanent disability, and waiver of premium death additional insurance; individual additional insurance products, including hospital cash plan, term, personal accident, and total permanent disability; and other insurance products, which includes national health protection, national defined protection, optimal protector eNational, and national credit life protection plus plans. The company was founded in 2017 and is based in Jakarta, Indonesia. PT Bhakti Multi Artha Tbk operates as a subsidiary of Pt Nasional Niaga Abadi.",
